<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sbḥwh wmjdwh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (sbḥwh wmjdwh wạrfʿwạ ạsmh ạlʿẓym
 bhtạf mlkwh mʿ ṣfwf ạlsmạỷyyn)2
 ạlqrạr - ạlmsyḥ qạm bạlḥqyqẗ qd qạm
 mḥṭmạ qwy̱ ạlsẖyṭạn wsạḥq ạlmwt bslṭạn
 2- (qdmwạ lh ạlsjwd ạlạ̹lh ạlḥq ạlạ̉myn
 mn fdạnạ wkẖlṣnạ bdmh ạlzky ạltẖmyn)2
 3- (ạnsẖdwạ ạḥly̱ ạlạngẖạm rnmwạ lmlknạ ạlmsyḥ
 fhw wḥdh mstḥq kl ạkrạm wtsbyḥ)2
 4- (hạ dẖbyḥẗ sẖkry̱ lh qd ạ̉qạmnạ bqyạmth
 wrfʿnạ fwq kl ḍʿf wạʿṭạnạ mn qwth)2</lyrics>
<author>kwrạl ạlʿdẖrạʾ ạ̉rḍ ạljwlf, kwrạl ạlʿdẖrạʾ ạ̉rḍ ạljwlf</author>
